# How to add github project to eclipse

Step 1. Create Github account 

Step 2. Start a Project = create a repository

Step 3. open perspectivie Git Repository 

Step 4. click on 'create a new git repository and add it to this view

Step 5. Create new project in eclipse

Step 6. share project > add to git repository

Step 7. Unstaged change -> Staged change -> commit and push
